  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decofarm is a small, clicker game about earning coins to upgrade a magical windmill. Each upgrade will unlock interesting buildings,  crops and other effects to grow your farm and decorate as you please. Enjoy 2-4 hours of playtime creating your dream farm filled with cute farm pets!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Clean up debris and expand your farm!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click to destroy various debris for coins. Coins can be used to expand your farm, upgrade your windmill or purchase numerous buildings, animals, crops and nature decorations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/089e7f64257dedf7cae1097107d8c695.poster.avif?t=1739738458\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/089e7f64257dedf7cae1097107d8c695.webm?t=1739738458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/089e7f64257dedf7cae1097107d8c695.mp4?t=1739738458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Unlock cute animals, crops, buildings and decorations!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock cats, dogs, chickens, sheep, cows and more by upgrading your windmill! All pets will automatically  earn  coins over time. Grow crops and harvest them for large amounts of coins. Decorate your farm to give bonus coin drops.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/d85ab7c08cf46e43493f62d2b7f2089a.poster.avif?t=1739738458\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/d85ab7c08cf46e43493f62d2b7f2089a.webm?t=1739738458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/d85ab7c08cf46e43493f62d2b7f2089a.mp4?t=1739738458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Look after your pets and keep them happy!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pet animals to grow their love! Leveling your animals love will boost the amount of coins they earn for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/9063745c1ab22282450939cdd0a053f4.poster.avif?t=1739738458\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/9063745c1ab22282450939cdd0a053f4.webm?t=1739738458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/9063745c1ab22282450939cdd0a053f4.mp4?t=1739738458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Build your own cozy farm!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase and place decorations as you like to create your own personalized farm. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/9ca1e156e36eadae85249c6cb53c565c.poster.avif?t=1739738458\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/9ca1e156e36eadae85249c6cb53c565c.webm?t=1739738458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/9ca1e156e36eadae85249c6cb53c565c.mp4?t=1739738458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decofarm is a small, clicker game about earning coins to upgrade a magical windmill. Each upgrade will unlock interesting buildings,  crops and other effects to grow your farm and decorate as you please. Enjoy 2-4 hours of playtime creating your dream farm filled with cute farm pets!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Clean up debris and expand your farm!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click to destroy various debris for coins. Coins can be used to expand your farm, upgrade your windmill or purchase numerous buildings, animals, crops and nature decorations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/089e7f64257dedf7cae1097107d8c695.poster.avif?t=1739738458\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/089e7f64257dedf7cae1097107d8c695.webm?t=1739738458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/089e7f64257dedf7cae1097107d8c695.mp4?t=1739738458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Unlock cute animals, crops, buildings and decorations!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock cats, dogs, chickens, sheep, cows and more by upgrading your windmill! All pets will automatically  earn  coins over time. Grow crops and harvest them for large amounts of coins. Decorate your farm to give bonus coin drops.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/d85ab7c08cf46e43493f62d2b7f2089a.poster.avif?t=1739738458\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/d85ab7c08cf46e43493f62d2b7f2089a.webm?t=1739738458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/d85ab7c08cf46e43493f62d2b7f2089a.mp4?t=1739738458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Look after your pets and keep them happy!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pet animals to grow their love! Leveling your animals love will boost the amount of coins they earn for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/9063745c1ab22282450939cdd0a053f4.poster.avif?t=1739738458\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/9063745c1ab22282450939cdd0a053f4.webm?t=1739738458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/9063745c1ab22282450939cdd0a053f4.mp4?t=1739738458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Build your own cozy farm!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase and place decorations as you like to create your own personalized farm. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/9ca1e156e36eadae85249c6cb53c565c.poster.avif?t=1739738458\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338530/extras/9ca1e156e36eadae85249c6cb53c565c.webm?t=1739738458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.aka